#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:117
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Hooking In the Emerge Process"
msgstr "emergeプロセスのフック"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:119
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Using /etc/portage/bashrc and affiliated files"
msgstr "/etc/portage/bashrcとその関連ファイルを使う"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:123
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"When Portage works with ebuilds, it uses a bash environment in which it calls\n"
"the various build functions (like src_prepare, src_configure, pkg_postinst,\n"
"etc.). But Portage also allows you to set up a bash environment yourself.\n"
msgstr ""
"Portageがebuildに従って処理を行うときは、bash環境内でsrc_prepareやsrc_configureやpkg_postinstなどのさまざまな関数を呼びます。\n"
"また、Portageは、そのbash環境を設定する機能も提供します。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:129
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The advantage of using your own bash environment is that you can hook in the\n"
"emerge process during each step it performs. This can be done for every emerge\n"
"(through <path>/etc/portage/bashrc</path>) or by using per-package environments\n"
"(through <path>/etc/portage/env</path> as discussed earlier).\n"
msgstr ""
"自分で独自のbash環境を設定する利点は、emergeの各段階にフックを入れることができるようになることです。\n"
"この設定は全てのemerge(<path>/etc/portage/bashrc</path>を使います)と個別のパッケージ(後述しますが<path>/etc/portage/env</path>を使います)に対して行えます。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:136
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To hook in the process, the bash environment can listen to the variables\n"
"<c>EBUILD_PHASE</c>, <c>CATEGORY</c> as well as the variables that are always\n"
"available during ebuild development (such as <c>P</c>, <c>PF</c>, ...). Based on\n"
"the values of these variables, you can then execute additional steps.\n"
msgstr ""
"emergeの各段階をフックするために、<c>EBUILD_PHASE</c>や<c>CATEGORY</c>\n"
"またebuildの開発プロセスで使うことができる全ての変数(<c>P</c>, <c>PF</c>など)にアクセスすることができます。\n"
"これらの変数に従って追加の処理を行なうことができるわけです。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:145
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Example: Updating File Databases"
msgstr "例: ファイルデータベースを更新する"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:149
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"In this example, we'll use <path>/etc/portage/bashrc</path> to call some file\n"
"database applications to ensure their databases are up to date with the system.\n"
"The applications used in the example are <c>aide</c> (an intrusion detection\n"
"tool) and <c>updatedb</c> (to use with <c>locate</c>), but these are meant as\n"
"examples. Do not consider this as a HOWTO for AIDE ;-)\n"
msgstr ""
"この例では、<path>/etc/portage/bashrc</path>を使い、\n"
"あるデータベースアプリケーションのデータベースがシステムの最新状態に沿うようにしています。\n"
"ここでは<c>aide</c>(侵入検知ツール)と<c>locate</c>に使うための<c>updatedb</c>とを使っていますが、\n"
"これはあくまでの例として選ばれたものです。\n"
"ここの例をAIDEのHOWTOだとは思わないでください。 ;-)\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:157
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To use <path>/etc/portage/bashrc</path> for this case, we need to \"hook\" in the\n"
"<c>postrm</c> (after removal of files) and <c>postinst</c> (after installation\n"
"of files) functions, because that is when the files on the file system have been\n"
"changed.\n"
msgstr ""
"<path>/etc/portage/bashrc</path>を使うには、この場合は\n"
"<c>postrm</c>(ファイルの削除の後)と<c>postinst</c>(ファイルのインストールの後)とをフックします。\n"
"この二つがファイルシステム上のファイルが変更される時だからです。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:163
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Example /etc/portage/bashrc"
msgstr "Example /etc/portage/bashrc"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:164
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"if [ \"${EBUILD_PHASE}\" == \"postinst\" ] || [ \"${EBUILD_PHASE}\" == \"postrm\" ];\n"
"then\n"
"  echo \":: Calling aide --update to update its database\";\n"
"  aide --update;\n"
"  echo \":: Calling updatedb to update its database\";\n"
"  updatedb;\n"
"fi\n"
msgstr ""
"if [ \"${EBUILD_PHASE}\" == \"postinst\"] || [ \"${EBUILD_PHASE}\" == \"postrm\" ];\n"
