"  echo \":: Calling aide --update to update its database\";\n"
"  aide --update;\n"
"  echo \":: Calling updatedb to update its database\";\n"
"  updatedb;\n"
"fi\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:178
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Executing Tasks After --sync"
msgstr "--syncの後にタスクを実行する"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:180
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "The /etc/portage/postsync.d location"
msgstr "/etc/portage/postsync.d"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:184
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Until now we've talked about hooking into the ebuild processes. However, Portage\n"
"also has another important function: updating the Portage tree. In order to run\n"
"tasks after updating the Portage tree, put a script inside\n"
"<path>/etc/portage/postsync.d</path> and make sure it is marked as executable.\n"
msgstr ""
"ここまではebuildの各段階をフックする方法について話してきました。\n"
"しかし、Portageにはもう一つ大事な機能、Portageツリーの更新があります。\n"
"Portageツリーの更新後にタスクを実行するには、\n"
"<path>/etc/portage/postsync.d</path>にスクリプトを置き実行可能にします。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:193
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Example: Running eix-update"
msgstr "例: eix-updateの実行"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:197
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you didn't use <c>eix-sync</c> to update the tree, you can still have its\n"
"database updated after running <c>emerge --sync</c> (or <c>emerge-webrsync</c>)\n"
"by putting a symlink to <path>/usr/bin/eix</path> called <path>eix-update</path>\n"
"in <path>/etc/portage/postsync.d</path>.\n"
msgstr ""
"Portageツリーの更新に<c>eix-sync</c>を使っていなくても、\n"
"<c>emerge --sync</c>(や<c>emerge-webrsync</c>)の後でeixのデータベースを更新することができます。\n"
"<path>/usr/bin/eix</path>から<path>/etc/portage/postsync.d</path>に<path>eix-update</path>という名でシンボリックリンクを作ってください。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:203
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Running eix-update after a sync operation"
msgstr "Running eix-update after a sync operation"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:204
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "# <i>ln -s /usr/bin/eix /etc/portage/postsync.d/eix-update</i>\n"
msgstr "# <i>ln -s /usr/bin/eix /etc/portage/postsync.d/eix-update</i>\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><note>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:208
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you rather use a different name, you will need to make a script that calls\n"
"<c>/usr/bin/eix-update</c> instead. The <c>eix</c> binary looks at how it has\n"
"been called to find out which function it has to execute. If you put in a\n"
"symlink to <c>eix</c> that isn't called <c>eix-update</c>, it will not run\n"
"correctly.\n"
msgstr ""
"<c>eix-update</c>以外の名前を使いたければ<c>/usr/bin/eix-update</c>を呼び出すスクリプトを作らなければなりません。\n"
"<c>eix</c>のバイナリはどういう名前で呼ばれたかによって、どの機能を実行するかを判定しています。\n"
"<c>eix-update</c>以外の名前で<c>eix</c>へのシンボリックリンクを作成しても、うまく動作しません。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:220
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Overriding Profile Settings"
msgstr "プロファイルの設定を上書きする"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:222
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "The /etc/portage/profile location"
msgstr "/etc/portage/profile"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:226
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"By default, Gentoo uses the settings contained in the profile pointed to by\n"
"<path>/etc/portage/make.profile</path> (a symbolic link to the right profile\n"
"directory). These profiles define both specific settings as well as inherit\n"
"settings from other profiles (through their <path>parent</path> file).\n"
msgstr ""
"デフォルトではGentooは<path>/etc/make.profile</path>\n"
"(ふさわしいプロファイルディレクトリへのシンボリックリンク)が指しているディレクトリ中の設定を使っています。\n"
"プロファイルの設定には、そのプロファイル特有の設定もあれば他のプロファイルから継承(<path>parent</path>ファイルで指定されています)したものもあります。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:233
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"By using <path>/etc/portage/profile</path>, you can override profile settings\n"
"such as <path>packages</path> (what packages are considered to be part of the\n"
"system set), forced use flags and more.\n"
msgstr ""
"<path>/etc/portage/profile</path>を使うことで、\n"
"<path>packages</path>(どのパッケージがsystem(基本システム)に含まれるか)や、\n"
"<path>virtuals</path>(virtualパッケージをインストールする時に実際にどのパッケージをデフォルトとしてインストールするか)などの設定を上書きすることができます。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:241
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Example: Adding nfs-utils to the System Set"
msgstr "例: nfs-utilsをsystem(基本システムパッケージ)に追加"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:245
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you use NFS-based file systems for rather critical file systems, you might\n"
"want to have <path>net-fs/nfs-utils</path> \"protected\" as a system package,\n"
"causing Portage to heavily warn you if it would be deleted.\n"
msgstr ""
"NFSベースのファイルシステムが必須であれば、\n"
"<path>net-fs/nfs-utils</path>を基本システムパッケージとして\"保護\"し、\n"
"削除される時にPortageにより強い警告を出してもらうようにしたくなるかもしれません。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:251
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To accomplish that, we add the package to\n"
"<path>/etc/portage/profile/packages</path>, prepended with a <c>*</c>:\n"
msgstr "これを実現するために、<c>*</c>を先頭につけてパッケージを<path>/etc/portage/profile/packages</path>に追記します。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:255
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/portage/profile/packages content"
msgstr "/etc/portage/profile/packages content"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:256
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "*net-fs/nfs-utils\n"
