msgid "Applying Non-Standard Patches"
msgstr "非標準のpatchをあてる"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:266
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Using epatch_user"
msgstr "epatch_userを使う"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:270
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To manage several ebuilds in a similar manner, ebuild developers use\n"
"<e>eclasses</e> (sort-of shell libraries) that define commonly used functions.\n"
"One of these eclasses is <path>eutils.eclass</path> which offers an interesting\n"
"function called <c>epatch_user</c>.\n"
msgstr ""
"ebuild開発者は<e>eclasses</e>(シェルのライブラリのようなもの)という共通して使われる関数を定義したものを使い、\n"
"様々なebuildを同じように扱っています。\n"
"そのeclaseの1つに<c>epathc_user</c>というおもしろい機能をもった<path>eutils.eclass</path>があります。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:277
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The <c>epatch_user</c> function applies source code patches that are found in\n"
"<path>/etc/portage/patches/&lt;category&gt;/&lt;package&gt;[-&lt;version&gt;[-&lt;revision&gt;]]</path>,\n"
"whatever directory is found first. Sadly, not all ebuilds automatically call\n"
"this function so just putting your patch in this location might not always work.\n"
msgstr ""
"関数<c>epatch_user</c>は、\n"
"<path>/etc/portage/patches/&lt;category&gt;/&lt;package&gt;[-&lt;version&gt;[-&lt;revision&gt;]]</path>にあるパッチを適用します。\n"
"複数のディレクトリがある場合は最初に見つかったものが適用されます。\n"
"残念ながら全てのebuildがこの関数を呼んでいるわけではないので、\n"
"パッチをこのディレクトリに置くだけでいつもうまく動くとは限りません。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:284
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Luckily, with the information provided above, you can call this function by\n"
"hooking into, for instance, the <c>prepare</c> phase. The function can be called\n"
"as many times as you like - it will only apply the patches once.\n"
msgstr ""
"幸いここまでで解説した情報を使えば、\n"
"この関数をたとえば<c>prepare</c>の段階でフックして呼ぶことができます。\n"
"この関数は何度呼んでもかまわないのです。何度呼んでもパッチは一度しか適用しません。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:292
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Example: Applying Patches to Firefox"
msgstr "例: Firefoxにパッチを適用する"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:296
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The <path>www-client/firefox</path> package is one of the few that already call\n"
"<c>epatch_user</c> from within the ebuild, so you do not need to override\n"
"anything specific. \n"
msgstr ""
"<path>www-client/firefox</path>はebuildの中で<c>epatch_user</c>を呼んでいる数少ないebuildの一つです。\n"
"なので、特になにも上書きするものはありません。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-portage-advanced.xml:302
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you need to patch firefox (for instance because a developer provided you with\n"
"a patch and asked you to check if it fixes the bug you reported), put the patch in\n"
"<path>/etc/portage/patches/www-client/firefox</path> (probably best to use the\n"
"full name, including version so that the patch does not interfere with later\n"
"versions) and rebuild firefox.\n"
msgstr ""
"Firefoxにパッチをあてる必要があるなら(たとえば開発者が、\n"
"あなたの報告したバグに対処するためにパッチをあてるように言ってきた時など)、\n"
"<path>/etc/portage/patches/www-client/firefox</path>\n"
"(おそらくバージョンもいれたフルネームを使い、\n"
"後のバージョンにパッチが影響しないようにするのが一番良いでしょう)\n"
"にそのパッチを置いて、Firefoxをリビルドします。\n"
